Feature: Session Management
  Scenario: User get direct session
    Given I am logged in as a user
    And I have a friend
    When I try to get a direct session with my friend
    Then I should retrieve it

  Scenario: User get a multimedia channel session
    Given I am logged in as a user
    And I am in server with a multimedia channel
    When I try to get a multimedia channel session
    Then I should retrieve it

  Scenario: User join a session
    Given I am logged in as a user
    And I have a session to join
    And I try to join the session
    Then I should be in the session

   Scenario: User leave a session
    Given I am logged in as a user
    And I have a session to leave
    And I try to leave the session
    Then I should not be in the session

